dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Nicholas Foster. May I have your name, please?
Hi Nicholas, my name is Angela Henderson.
Nice to meet you, Angela. Could you please provide me with your policy number for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is five six eight two three zero.
Thank you, Angela. I also need to confirm your date of birth. Can you tell me your birthdate?
My birthdate is the eleventh of June, nineteen eighty-five.
Great, thank you for confirming, Angela. Is there anything specific I can assist you with today regarding your policy or any claims?
I'd like to inquire about adding a new vehicle to my policy.
Of course, Angela. Let's discuss the details. Thank you for providing the information. Is there anything else I can help you with today?
Thank you for your time, Angela. Have a wonderful day and drive safe.
